    - "concurrent.futures.__package__.__len__() == 18. 'concurrent.futures' is 18 chars: 'concurrent'=10 + '.'=1 + 'futures'=7 = 18. __package__ equals __name__ for packages. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
